<Content_wSideColumn ID="x36059" Name="FAQ" Layout="byuidefault.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Frequently Asked Questions</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">questions answered</Abstract><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="SideColumn" label="L/R Column" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><MoveLeft type="boolean" label="Toggle column right or left (right is default)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</MoveLeft><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="ImageComponent" label="Image Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="LeftColumnImageComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="TextComponent" label="Text Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="ColumnTextComponent"/><fbookTop type="boolean" label="Put facebook at top of page" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</fbookTop><fbookStatus type="string" label="Facebook ID#" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookStatus><fbookDisplayed type="string" label="Number of facebook messages to display" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">1</fbookDisplayed></xPower><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p><em style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Q</strong></em></p>
<p align="justify" style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><em style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"> -<strong> Will students be able to print to campus printers while connected to the wireless network?</strong></em></p>
<p align="justify" style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">A - Yes, students will be able to print to campus network printers.&nbsp; Visit&nbsp;<em style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><a href="http://www.byui.edu/help-desk/categories/wireless-printing" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #00254a; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Student Tech Home</a> </em>for a wireless printing tutorial</strong>.</p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Q</strong> -&nbsp;<em style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Why are students required to have laptops if they are not used in every class?</em></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">A - Laptop benefits extend away from the classroom, but will also include an every growing number of classroom uses as the requirement matures and more courses grow into the use of this educational option.</strong></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Q</strong> - My major does not seem technical, why should I have a laptop<em style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">?</em></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">A - Every field increasingly depends upon technology.&nbsp; Owning and working with a laptop increases personal abilities to work with and understand technology in ways that casual use does not.&nbsp; Laptops can assist in preparing students&nbsp;for the competitive job marketplace.</strong></p>
